responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "402B70C34A4B9D0621F770838E3146D8", "My tribe. The Minotaur of what you folk call The Riverlands. The Ashen Flame will rule here, in time. You godlings will recede like the tide before our might. For now, though, we abide by your presence. Were I not in my present dolor, though, you would know the fear that is your birthright.")
